      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 it is best suited for buyers looking for a project car, a parts donor, or someone with mechanical expertise willing to invest in repairs. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple dents, deep scratches, rust spots, and heavily faded paint. The interior is worn throughout, with torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and a general sense of long, hard use. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require substantial work to return to reliable daily-driver status \u2014 it may start and move, but it should not be considered dependable transportation without significant investment. We are pricing this vehicle accordingly and encourage all interested buyers to inspect it in person or have a trusted mechanic evaluate it before purchase. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Rare find alert \u2014 this one is truly exceptional! This vehicle is in mint condition, meaning it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, from the spotless interior to the gleaming exterior with zero visible wear. The mechanicals are in perfect working order, and you'd be hard-pressed to find a cleaner example anywhere on the market. If you've been waiting for the best, your wait is over!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. This is a truly exceptional example that stands out even among well-maintained used cars. The exterior is virtually flawless, with a deep, glossy finish free of scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, seals, and moldings are intact and pristine. The interior is equally impressive: the seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces show no meaningful wear, staining, or fading. All electronics, infotainment features, climate controls, and power accessories function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, with no leaks, corrosion, or deferred maintenance. The car has been serviced meticulously, and all fluids, filters, and wear items are in excellent shape. It drives with confidence \u2014 smooth, quiet, and responsive \u2014 exactly as you'd hope from a vehicle of this caliber. If you're looking for a used car that feels as close to new as possible without paying new-car prices, this is a rare opportunity. We invite you to inspect it in person; it will not disappoint.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition and is priced to reflect that honestly \u2014 please read the full description before reaching out. The car runs and drives, making it a functional option for a buyer who needs reliable basic transportation, but it comes with several notable imperfections. On the exterior, you'll find multiple scratches, a few small-to-medium dents, and some paint fading, particularly on the hood and roof. The interior shows clear signs of age and use: the upholstery is worn, there are stains on the seats, and some trim pieces are loose or cracked. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs, but buyers should be aware that some maintenance items are overdue \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. The tires have adequate tread remaining, and the brakes are functional, though not recently serviced. This is an honest, as-is sale priced for someone who understands they may need to invest some additional money to bring the vehicle fully up to standard. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
