      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? Here's your chance! This vehicle is priced to honestly reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and will require meaningful repairs and attention to get back on the road reliably. That said, it's a great candidate for someone with mechanical skills or a vision for restoration. Priced affordably so you have room in your budget to put in the work. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
